dcterms:description: A new dataset called AcneSCU, which has higher-resolution and more normalized imageries, more fine-grained acne categories, and more precise annotations than previous acne datasets. AcneSCU consists of 276 facial images shot by VISIA complexion analysis system with 31777 instance segmentation annotations of 10 lesion categories.
dcterms:title: AcneSCU
